<item>
            <title>[LU-7141] sanity-quota test_21 hangs in dd</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7141</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-quota test 21 times out while writing repeatedly to a file using dd. Logs for this time out are at &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/8d0246a2-57b7-11e5-a084-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/8d0246a2-57b7-11e5-a084-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the client(2) console log, we see&lt;/p&gt;
